## ğŸ—ƒ Output Structure

```
output_dir/
â”œâ”€â”€ images/              # Raw Sentinel-2
â”œâ”€â”€ Resampled/           # 10m resampled bands
â”œâ”€â”€ stack/               # Stacked Sentinel-2 bands
â”œâ”€â”€ DEM/                 # Elevation data
â”œâ”€â”€ GRD/                 # Raw Sentinel-1 GRD
â”œâ”€â”€ GRD_Extracted/       # Extracted by bounding box
â”œâ”€â”€ Clipped_SAR/         # Matched SAR chips
â”œâ”€â”€ stacked_with_sar/    # Combined S2 + SAR + DEM
â”œâ”€â”€ mask/                # Binary masks (from lakes)
â”œâ”€â”€ normalize/           # Final normalized image chips
â”œâ”€â”€ AOI_boxes/           # AOI boxes (GeoJSONs)
â””â”€â”€ shapefile/each/      # Individual AOI shapefiles
```

---

## ğŸ§ª Example Use Cases

- Glacial lake mapping and segmentation
- Flood extent extraction
- Multimodal image fusion (S2+S1+DEM)
- Chip-based data generation for training transformers and GANs

